      },
      "date": "2011-08-10 07:15:52.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nJinshan,\nif there really is no benefit to permanently reducing the lu_object cache size on the client, then best to go with this original patch.\n\nI apologize for leading you around in a circle, but I wasn't aware that lu_object cache is used for anything important on the client at all.  If making a small cache on the client will affect performance for real-world uses, then best to leave the default size alone and only use the module parameter for testing.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
